Tyler Perry's The Haves and the Have Nots

Jeffery tells Wyatt that the man he hit is Hanna's son. Elsewhere, Candace finds 

out that Benny is in the county hospital and that the doctors want to take him

off life support, so she begs Jim to move him to a private hospital.
